{"tid":856623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明日大嶼係為咗「下一代」嘅基建呀","createTime":"2018-10-10T16:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:36:08.000Z","uid":390,"like":151,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"42fbea938adcfbe8fd3666de1372b3ad6af43486","tid":856623,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"我唔做環保撚唔講保育！<br />\n我唔做炒賣撚唔講財團！<br />\n我唔做數學撚唔講造價！<br />\n剩係想講，一個人工島要起幾耐？<br />\n廿年？三十年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦，你話為下一代著想<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁依家要結婚生仔置業嘅人呢？<br />\n全部仆街陷家剷齊齊訓街最好啦<br />\n唔撚去解決呢一刻已經有嘅急切住屋需求<br />\n反而去諗胚胎都未撚成型嘅「下一代」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你依家每日放百五隻蝗蟲入嚟蠶食香港<br />\n廿年後接近110萬隻！<br />\n起嚟比班腥港人住<br />\n淋病奶共產袋底會唔會奶得透徹咗少少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去<br />\n香港根本就冇所謂嘅「下一代」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30dd29b785e9a1238d86a2bc984119680baff092","tid":856623,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf4b0475b16507193c1be510856da2d6f79333b","tid":856623,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e514182b4af10c14e868d034705190968ca24362","tid":856623,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:10